    "title": "Bewakoof is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bewakoof! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Dhanbad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bewakoof:\nBewakoof is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bewakoof!",
